      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That failure doesn't mean failure at all, because your worth isn't defined by money or the company that collapsed while you learned to fire up a survival engine for tomorrow.\nYou go home and tell your parents you made a sacrifice that was supposed to be a lesson, not a disaster that defines a life that doesn't need them anymore.\nThe noise that screams of ruin is just a shell that you pick up and throw away until reality finally listens to the quiet you can lead yourself back to.",
