      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your worth remains intact despite the wreckage, proving that a single broken foundation cannot destroy a lifetime of personal strength you possess long before the lawsuits began.\nThe path forward is paved with small, concrete steps like drafting a repayment plan or turning down calls, which will slowly tear the illusion of permanence right away.\nThis is not a fairy tale but a hard fight where your survival is the only victory that matters, and you are stronger than this crushing weight ever gave you credit for.",
